attribute.dc:comment: This is a collection of attributes meant to display the FAIR aspects in the questionnaire.
Content related to the fundability along the FAIR data principles.
Content related to data accessibility along the FAIR data principles.
Content related to the interoperability of data along the FAIR data principles.
Content related to the reusability of project data along the FAIR data principles.
Refers to a detailed description of data to which the FAIR principles apply.
This attribute corresponds to input needed from other data providers.
